title: FNDA Breaks Above 200-Day Moving Average - Bullish for FNDA - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, shares of the FNDA ETF (Symbol: FNDA) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $36.81, changing hands as high as $37.30 per share. FNDA shares are currently trading up about 2.4% on the day. The chart below shows the one year performance of FNDA shares, versus its 200 day moving average:     Looking at the chart above, FNDA's low point in its 52 week range is $30.9833 per share, with $41.59 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $37.32.
